03:29.190 --> 03:31.010
Bagus, makanlah.

03:31.190 --> 03:32.110
Jangan makan.

03:33.120 --> 03:34.910
Spekulasi kata kerja modal.

03:37.190 --> 03:38.720
Spekulasi yang mengiakan.

03:39.400 --> 03:40.400
Awak tak tahukah?

03:42.400 --> 03:45.190
"Must have done", bacalah tiga kali.

03:45.190 --> 03:46.650
Jika tidak, jangan makan.

03:47.190 --> 03:50.030
Ramainya orang di sini.

03:50.030 --> 03:51.360
"Must have done"!

03:51.360 --> 03:52.910
"Must have done"!

03:55.000 --> 03:56.620
"Must have done"!

03:56.640 --> 03:58.280
"Must have done"!

03:58.590 --> 03:59.800
"Must have done"!

03:59.800 --> 04:00.400
Sekali lagi!

04:00.400 --> 04:01.590
"Must have done"!

04:01.590 --> 04:02.120
Sekali lagi!

04:02.120 --> 04:03.680
"Must have done"!

04:03.680 --> 04:04.720
Sudahlah.

04:04.750 --> 04:06.710
- Makan.
- Makan.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.280
Bagus.

04:14.960 --> 04:15.840
Cikgu Lin!

04:20.070 --> 04:22.360
Bagaimana dengan keadaan
pasukan bola sepak baru-baru ini?

04:22.360 --> 04:23.160
Agak bagus.

04:24.240 --> 04:25.050
