04:27.390 --> 04:29.990
Awak mesti perhatikan
keadaan mental mereka.

04:32.470 --> 04:34.130
Penyelia Qian, jangan risau.

04:36.080 --> 04:36.820
Baiklah.

04:39.000 --> 04:40.659
