04:41.300 --> 04:42.510
"In the long run".

04:43.800 --> 04:45.270
"In the long run".

04:46.800 --> 04:48.120
"Run out of" (kehabisan).

04:48.120 --> 04:49.750
"Run out of".

04:50.159 --> 04:51.630
"Run out of".

04:53.830 --> 04:55.690
