04:59.240 --> 05:01.330
Saya pandang rendah terhadap awak.

05:01.430 --> 05:03.390
- Awak juga.
- Saya?

05:03.390 --> 05:04.680
- Memanglah awak.
- Awak, bukan saya.

05:04.680 --> 05:08.190
- Awak...
- Awak...

05:08.190 --> 05:09.870
Awak.

05:09.870 --> 05:12.270
