10:30.480 --> 10:31.010
Baiklah.

10:34.630 --> 10:37.290
Si Jin mahu buat apa lagi?

10:37.390 --> 10:39.480
Tak apa, kami menemani awak pergi ke sana.

10:39.480 --> 10:40.240
Jalan.

10:40.240 --> 10:41.840
Dia jumpa saya pasti tiada hal baik.

10:41.840 --> 10:43.780
Saya benar-benar tak sudi jumpa dia.

10:43.780 --> 10:44.910
Awak tak sudi jumpa dia,

10:44.910 --> 10:46.080
