14:41.390 --> 14:42.260
Fu.

14:42.750 --> 14:44.520
Kita dah menang kali ini.

14:45.440 --> 14:46.900
"Anak" saya dah membesar.

14:47.540 --> 14:49.240
Sudahlah.

14:50.000 --> 14:50.750
Menang.

14:50.750 --> 14:52.120
Kita dah menang.

14:53.390 --> 14:55.170
Menang!

14:55.190 --> 14:56.990
Menang!

14:57.010 --> 14:59.630
Menang!

15:00.030 --> 15:01.550
- Cikgu Lin.
- Helo, Cikgu Lin.

15:01.550 --> 15:02.510
Cikgu Lin.

15:03.790 --> 15:04.550
Cikgu Lin.

15:05.120 --> 15:06.270
Awak "tik tik" saya,

15:06.270 --> 15:08.110
